west to Alaska, south to Michigan. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[797,851,1075,1100]" pageId="148" pageNumber="149">
<collectingCountry box="[797,851,1075,1100]" name="United States of America" pageId="148" pageNumber="149">USA</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
: AK, ME, MI. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1015,1132,1075,1100]" pageId="148" pageNumber="149">
<collectingCountry box="[1015,1132,1075,1100]" name="Canada" pageId="148" pageNumber="149">CANADA</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
: AB, BC, NB, NS, NT, ON, PE, SK.
</paragraph>
